Package org.planit.io.project

Class PlanItProject

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.planit.project.CustomPlanItProject
      • org.planit.io.project.PlanItProject
  • public class PlanItProject
extends CustomPlanItProject
    PLANit project which is nothing more than a CustomPlanItProject without any custom configuration pre-embedded. So, it allows maximum flexibility for users. It does assume the PLANit default input format and registers the PLANit default output formatter automtically
    Author:
    markr, gman6028
